The '''Bridge of Unity''' was a bridge across the [[Glitannai Esplanade]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. Its lower levels contained high-class restaurants. It was destroyed when the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] took the planet and began [[Terraforming/Legends|Vongforming]] it.<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

